org.jtrim2.taskgraph

Class TaskNodeKey<R,I>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jtrim2.taskgraph.TaskNodeKey<R,I>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - the return type of the function of the associated task node
    I - the type of the argument passed to the task node factory when requested for the node to be created

    public final class TaskNodeKey<R,I>
extends Object
    Defines the key uniquely identifying a particular task node.

    Thread safety

    This class is immutable (with the assumption that the factory argument is also immutable, and as such, its methods can be safely accessed from multiple concurrent threads.

    Synchronization transparency

    The methods of this class are synchronization transparent.
    See Also:
    TaskGraphBuilder, TaskFactoryKey
